	<h1 class="title">鬼才虚渊玄又带着他的新作来了，这次是霹雳布袋戏</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/495481/small/495481.jpg?1456747733" alt="">
